arts.ttl: Dynamo's Jimmy Maurer, Sounders' Stefan Frei duel to scoreless draw
arts.sum: Jimmy Maurer finished with four saves in his first start for Houston and Seattleâ€™s Stefan Frei stopped the only shot he faced as the Dynamo and Sounders played to a scoreless draw at Lumen Field on Saturday night. Frei finished off his first clean sheet of the season and the 100th of his career with the Sounders (1-2-2) in his fourth start this season.

arts.ttl: Adidas to Release MLS Third Kits for 5 MLS Teams: Inter Miami, Seattle Sounders, FC Dallas, Real Salt Lake, and Toronto FC
arts.sum: Footy Headlines can leak that Adidas will launch the MLS 2025 third kits for 5 teams, including 4 new teams compared to MLS 2024 including: Inter Miami (old from 2024), Seattle Sounders, FC Dallas, Real Salt Lake and Toronto FC.
